# Methodology applicability node – links a methodology to its applicability rationale

<https://nova.org.za/novaimpactaccountingstandard/methodology-applicability/ma-001>
    a nias-o:MethodologyApplicability ;
    nias-o:usesMethodology <https://nova.org.za/novaimpactaccountingstandard/methodologies/NIAS-SOLAR-001> ;
    nias-o:applicabilityRationale "The NIAS-SOLAR-001 methodology is applicable because the project replaces fossil-fuel combustion with solar PV generation, matching the eligible technology category and geographic scope defined in the methodology." .

